<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>反编译 on 编程心语</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/tags/%E5%8F%8D%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91/</link><description>Recent content in 反编译 on 编程心语</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2013 20:23:33 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ithome.me/tags/%E5%8F%8D%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>myeclipse8以上安装反编译插件</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2013/03/19/myeclipse8%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8D%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/</link><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2013 20:23:33 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2013/03/19/myeclipse8%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8D%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;首先需要准备两个东西&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;准备工作： 1、下载jad.exe文件：&lt;a href="http://www.varaneckas.com/jad" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;http://www.varaneckas.com/jad&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、下载jadeclipse插件：&lt;a href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/jadclipse/files/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;http://sourceforge.net/projects/jadclipse/files/&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;安装如下：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、将jadeclipse插件net.sf.jadclipse_3.3.0.jar 拷贝到myeclipse安装目录MyEclipsedropins目录下，比如E:MyEclipseMyEclipse 9dropins目录下,重启myeclipse&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>